The following benchmark is of 109 ODEs and 188 parameters that describe a stiff SBML model, modelling the EGFR signalling between normal and NSCLC cells Bidkhori et al.. It is referenced from Biomodels Database, and the model was parsed to Julia are finally to ODEs using ModelingToolkit.
